original_title: AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト200 2014
overview: The AKB48 Request Hour Setlist Best 200 2014 (AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト200 2014) was held from January 23 to January 26, 2014 at Tokyo Dome City Hall, and then on April 6th, 2014 at Saitama Super Arena. Fans made their voices heard by voting for their favorite AKB48/SKE48/NMB48/HKT48/SDN48 original songs.
title: AKB48 Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2014
